## Problem Generators (generators/)
- [ ] `eigen_generator.py` – A = PDP⁻¹ with distinct integer eigenvalues
- [ ] `calculus_generator.py` – clean polynomial/rational function problems

## Solver Modules (solvers/)
- [ ] `eigen_solver.py` – characteristic polynomial → eigenvalues → eigenvectors
- [ ] `cayley_hamilton_solver.py` – verify CH theorem, compute inverse
- [ ] `quadratic_form_solver.py` – orthogonal reduction to canonical form
- [ ] `limit_continuity_solver.py` – L'Hôpital's rule steps
- [ ] `partial_derivative_solver.py` – Euler's theorem verification
- [ ] `jacobian_solver.py` – Jacobian matrix & functional dependence
- [ ] `taylor_maclaurin_solver.py` – multivariable Taylor/Maclaurin expansion
- [ ] `maxima_minima_solver.py` – critical points + Lagrange multipliers
- [ ] `definite_integral_solver.py` – Leibniz rule differentiation under integral
- [ ] `multiple_integral_solver.py` – double/triple integral evaluation
- [ ] `variable_change_solver.py` – Cartesian ↔ polar/spherical change of variables
- [ ] `linear_ode_solver.py` – 2nd-order constant-coefficient ODE

## UI Layer
- [ ] `app.py` – main Streamlit app with session-state machine + topic selector

